♪Dengarlah, suara pasang surut air♪

128
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,550
♪Sedang mengatakan, "aku bersedia"♪

129
00:05:14,790 --> 00:05:19,130
♪Matahari senja mendengar bisikanmu♪

130
00:05:19,130 --> 00:05:24,290
♪Terlalu banyak rahasia
Kuceritakan padamu♪

131
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:27,270
♪Terlalu manis♪

132
